title: Introduction to python programming
description: Enhance your python skills from scratch by enrolling into this course and become a professional.
expectation:
Become a Python Pro.
Make 100 projects in 100 days. 
Become a python professional. 
Get all the required knowledge about python programming language.
requirement: A laptop / computer with windows os or maos or linux to be installed.
eligibility: No need to have prior knowledge of programming here everything will be thought from scratch.
content:
1) Intro to Python. 
2) Intermediate Python. 
3) Advanced Python.
